Type:

The cement pouring panel comprises specially prepared concrete raw materials through pouring and molding. Its core is fiber-reinforced concrete and ultra-light composite materials, and a protective film is sprayed on the surface. On the premise of maintaining the original concrete texture, our cement pouring panel achieves a more efficient and convenient installation effect than concrete. It is more durable and weather-resistant and has a wide range of applications, including the interior and exterior walls and ceilings of commercial spaces such as office buildings, hotels, and exhibition halls.
